description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Beverly Hills and Real Housewives of New York. On RHOBH, we get a beautifully insane dinner party with a lot of secrets and a stoned Mauricio. On RHONY, the women head to Fashion Week, Tinsley gets her "IT" back, and Sonja shows off her grey sweatpant collection.
